data.description: Welcome to 106 7th St, Elizabeth located near buses, shopping centers and directly across from Trinitas Hospital. This cash cow & income producing property its an Investors dream. Amazing opportunity to live-in or investment. This two-family home is renovated and ready for move in. 1st floor features Large eat-in kitchen, Livingroom, 2 bedrooms and 1 bath. 2nd floor 3 bedrooms 1 bath. Bonus finished attic separate entrance and full finished walk-out basement. Private gated driveway with concrete poured backyard perfect for entertaining. Property is being sold AS IS. Buyer responsible for obtaining CO & Fire Certificate.
